bib_record.title: Relativistic medium effects for 208Pb(p,p') at intermediate energies

free_txt: Analyzing power for the inclusive quasifree (p,p)
reaction on Pb-208 at 290 MeV are presented.
- by compiler - some experimental data are not shown on
the figures.  These data are presented as DATA-MIN.
A 51 mg/cm**2 Pb-208 target was used.
